io.swagger

Interface HomeAutomationServerConnector

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    FHEMConnector

    public interface HomeAutomationServerConnector
    The Interface HomeAutomationServerConnector. This interface provides the methods to connect a home automation server connector class to the endpoints. Therefore the connector class, i.e. FHEMConnector, has to implement this interface and get annotated as '@Service'.
